{"word":"H4843 - מָרַר - mârar - maw-rar' - Bitter - கசப்பான","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>מָרַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mârar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-rar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bitter / கசப்பான"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசனமாயிரு, மனக்கிலேசமாகு, துக்கமாயிரு, கசப்பாயிரு, சஞ்சலப்படு, மனமடிவாக்கு, துக்கித்திரு, கடுங்கோபங்கொள், கோபப்படுத்து, கசப்பாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(1) to be bitter"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be bitter"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to show bitterness"},{"paragraph":"2) to make bitter"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to make bitter, embitter"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hithpalpel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to embitter oneself"},{"paragraph":"2) to be enraged"},{"paragraph":"(2) to be strong, to strengthen"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>trickle</i> (see <a href=\"#/H4752 - מַר - mar - mar/4752\">H4752</a>); but used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H4751 - מַר - mar - mar/4751\">H4751</a>; to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>bitter</i> (literally or figuratively): - (be, be in, deal, have, make) bitter (-ly, -ness), be moved with choler, (be, have sorely, it) grieved (-eth), provoke, vex."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4470 - מֶמֶר - memer - meh'-mer/4470\">H4470</a>, <a href=\"#/H4472 - מַמְרֹר - mamrôr - mam-rore'/4472\">H4472</a>, <a href=\"#/H4751 - מַר - mar - mar/4751\">H4751</a>, <a href=\"#/H4753 - מֹר - môr - more/4753\">H4753</a>, <a href=\"#/H4755 - מָרָא - Mârâʼ - maw-raw'/4755\">H4755</a>, <a href=\"#/H4785 - מָרָה - Mârâh - maw-raw'/4785\">H4785</a>, <a href=\"#/H4786 - מֹרָה - môrâh - mo-raw'/4786\">H4786</a>, <a href=\"#/H4787 - מׇרָּה - morrâh - mor-raw'/4787\">H4787</a>, <a href=\"#/H4814 - מְרִירוּת - mᵉrîyrûwth - mer-ee-rooth'/4814\">H4814</a>, <a href=\"#/H4815 - מְרִירִי - mᵉrîyrîy - mer-ee-ree'/4815\">H4815</a>, <a href=\"#/H4843 - מָרַר - mârar - maw-rar'/4843\">H4843</a>, <a href=\"#/H4844 - מְרֹר - mᵉrôr - mer-ore'/4844\">H4844</a>, <a href=\"#/H4845 - מְרֵרָה - mᵉrêrâh - mer-ay-raw'/4845\">H4845</a>, <a href=\"#/H4846 - מְרֹרָה - mᵉrôrâh - mer-o-raw'/4846\">H4846</a>, <a href=\"#/H4847 - מְרָרִי - Mᵉrârîy - mer-aw-ree'/4847\">H4847</a>, <a href=\"#/H4848 - מְרָרִי - Mᵉrârîy - mer-aw-ree'/4848\">H4848</a>, <a href=\"#/H8563 - תַּמְרוּר - tamrûwr - tam-roor'/8563\">H8563</a>"}]}